===Talking to Alrena after getting the gas mask===
* '''Alrena:''' Hello darling, I think Edmond had a good idea of how to get into West Ardougne, you should hear his idea.
* '''Player:''' Alright, I'll go and see him now.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Edmond after getting the gas mask===
* '''Player:''' Hi Edmond, I've got the gas mask now.
* '''Edmond:''' Good stuff, now for the digging. Beneath us are the Ardougne sewers. I've done some research, and I reckon you can use them to enter West Ardougne.
* '''Edmond:''' I've already tried digging down to them but the soil is rock hard. You'll need to pour on several buckets of water to soften it up. I reckon four buckets should do it.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Edmond before pouring water on the mud patch===
* '''Edmond:''' How's it going?
* '''Player:''' I still need to pour four more buckets of water on the soil.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Alrena before pouring water on the mud patch===
* '''Player:''' Hello Alrena.
* '''Alrena:''' Hello darling, how's that tunnel coming along?
* '''Player:''' I just need to soften the soil and then we'll start digging.
* '''Alrena:''' Well I'm sure you're quicker than Edmond.
* {{tact|end}}

