===Talking to Mourner or Head Mourner in West Ardougne===
* '''Mourner:''' Hmmm, how did you get over here? You're not one of this rabble. Ah well, you'll have to stay. Can't risk you going back now.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|So what's a mourner?}}
** '''Player:''' So what's a mourner?
** '''Mourner:''' We're working for King Lathas of East Ardougne. He has tasked us with containing the accursed plague sweeping West Ardougne.
** '''Mourner:''' We also do our best to ease these people's suffering. We're nicknamed mourners because we spend a lot of time at plague victim funerals, no one else is allowed to risk attending.
** '''Mourner:''' It's a demanding job, and we get little thanks from the people here.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I haven't got the plague though...}}
** '''Player:''' I haven't got the plague though...
** '''Mourner:''' Can't risk you being a carrier. That protective clothing you have isn't regulation issue. It won't meet safety standards.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I'm looking for a woman named Elena.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm looking for a woman named Elena.
** '''Mourner:''' Ah yes, I've heard of her. A healer I believe. She must be mad coming over here voluntarily.
** '''Mourner:''' I hear rumours she has probably caught the plague now. Very tragic, a stupid waste of life.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Ted Rehnison before getting the book from Jethick===
* '''Ted Rehnison:''' Go away. We don't want any.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Jethick if the player does not have Elena's picture===
* '''Jethick:''' Hello, I don't recognise you. We don't get many newcomers around here.
* '''Player:''' How come?
* '''Jethick:''' The plague of course. Not many people want to come to a place like this and the few that do normally get stopped by the mourners.
* '''Jethick:''' All you'll find here now are the dead and the dying. Even our own king has abandoned us.
* '''Player:''' Your king?
* '''Jethick:''' Yes, King Tyras of West Ardougne. He's the brother of King Lathas, the ruler of East Ardougne.
* '''Player:''' So where is the king?
* '''Jethick:''' Well he's always been a bit of an explorer. He's led multiple expeditions into the uncharted lands to the west.
* '''Jethick:''' The plague first started when he came back from one of these expeditions. More than a few suspect that some of his men caught it out there and brought it back with them.
* '''Jethick:''' The king didn't care though. He just left on another expedition to the west. He hasn't been seen since. He left the city warder Bravek in charge but he's no better.
* '''Jethick:''' Anyway, you clearly didn't come here to talk about kings. So tell me, what brings you to West Ardougne?
* '''Player:''' I'm looking for a woman from East Ardougne called Elena.
* '''Jethick:''' East Ardougnian women are easier to find in East Ardougne. Not many would come to West Ardougne to find one. Although the name is familiar, what does she look like?
* '''Player:''' Um... brown hair... in her twenties...
* '''Jethick:''' Hmmm, that doesn't narrow it down a huge amount... I'll need to know more than that, or see a picture?
* {{tact|end}}

